window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I was stranded in a snowstorm with my ex's pro hockey player dad. Now, I'm pregnant.</b></p> <p>After a nasty breakup with my ex, his dad takes pity on me and offers to drive me home.</p> <p>But when a snowstorm strands us in the middle of nowhere, we're forced to find a roadside motel with nothing to do… but each other.</p> <p>There's only one tiny bed... and he's huge.</p> <p>We wake up the next morning tangled like pretzels. My face nuzzled in his chest. His rock-hard hockey stick poking between my legs.</p> <p>He says he's too old for me and nothing can ever happen between us. I am his son's ex-girlfriend, after all.</p> <p>But now, I have a secret that could change everything… I'm having his baby.</p>"; 
